   Julian Lennon says he's just like his late
father, short-tempered and cynical.
   ``I have the same wit, the same sense of humor,'' Lennon said in
the Sept. 8-10 issue of USA Weekend.
   ``And I'm very aggressive and opinionated; I have very strong
beliefs, as he did,'' Lennon said of his father, John Lennon, who
left Julian's mother to marry Yoko Ono.
