72 fair; Jacksonville 75 partly cloudy; Key West 84 fair; Knoxville
69 fair; Macon 73 cloudy; Miami 81 fair; New York 59 fair;
Philadelphia 64 fair; Pittsburgh 69 foggy; Portland, Maine 56 foggy;
Richmond 63 foggy; Tampa 77 fair; Washington, D.C. 68 foggy.
   _Central: Birmingham 72 partly cloudy; Bismarck 54 fair; Chicago
70 partly cloudy; Denver 59 fair; Des Moines 70 thunderstorms; Fort
Worth 82 fair; Indianapolis 69 foggy; Kansas City 77 fair; Little
Rock 75 hazy; Louisville 71 foggy; Memphis 75 fair; Nashville 68
fair; New Orleans 74 fair; North Platte 65 cloudy; Oklahoma City 75
fair; Omaha 70 cloudy; Rapid City 58 cloudy; St. Louis 77 fair;
Minneapolis-St. Paul 57 fair; Sault Ste. Marie 65 foggy; San Antonio
77 fair.
   _West: Albuquerque 66 partly cloudy; Anchorage 56 cloudy; Boise
58 partly cloudy; Casper 58 cloudy; Fairbanks 60 cloudy; Great Falls
50 cloudy; Honolulu 78 fair; Las Vegas 76 fair; Los Angeles 62 fair;
Medford 62 fair; Pendleton 59 fair; Phoenix 91 partly cloudy;
