the Medellin cocaine cartel, to be arraigned before federal
magistrate.
   Grand Rapids, Mich. _ Jury selection in Walker nursing home
deaths trial.
   Oakland, Calif _ Pleading by man accused of killing Huey Newton.
   Los Angeles _ Zsa Zsa Gabor faces trial on charges of slapping a
motorcycle cop.
   Jacksonville, Fla. _ Son-of-Lehder trial opens in federal court.
